title: Søren Wærenskjold, Lotte Claes Defy All Expectations with Victory in Omloop Nieuwsblad Races
content:
Young Norwegian Wærenskjold outsprints Magnier and Philipsen to the line, Claes beats Nerlo after day-long breakaway in women's race.

Read the full article at Søren Wærenskjold, Lotte Claes Defy All Expectations with Victory in Omloop Nieuwsblad Races on Velo.
